    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or an ultra-budget ride? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it has significant wear, and you should expect mechanical and cosmetic issues that will need attention. It's not a turnkey solution, but for the right buyer \u2014 whether you're a DIY enthusiast or just need something to tinker with \u2014 it could be a rewarding find! Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for your needs and skills.",
